text: Andrew Bruce Wallace (born 27 February 1968) is an Australian politician. He is the 31st Speaker of the House of Representatives since 2021. He is a member of the Liberal Party. He has been a member of the House of Representatives since 2016. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Speakers of the Australian House of Representatives Category:Politicians from Queensland Category:Politicians from Melbourne
